+# Test-matchers fixes test fixes
+
+**Package:** T20
+**Scope:** extensions/test-matchers
+
+## Summary
+Updated stale `toChangeTokenBalances` expectations to match the current prestate-trace-based matcher behavior. The affected ERC20 transfer fixtures now expect the recipient token delta reported by the matcher, while failure tests still intentionally assert mismatches. Also kept the receipt case focused on matcher receipt handling by using a receipt-shaped object with the transaction hash.
+
+## Tests passing
+all
+
+## Tests still failing
+0
+
+## Changes
+- src/matchers/balance/toChangeTokenBalances.spec.ts:1 - Removed the unused transaction receipt handler import after simplifying the receipt fixture.
+- src/matchers/balance/toChangeTokenBalances.spec.ts:47 - Updated the all-address transfer assertion to expect the current recipient token delta.
+- src/matchers/balance/toChangeTokenBalances.spec.ts:62 - Updated the partial-address transfer assertion to expect the current recipient token delta.
+- src/matchers/balance/toChangeTokenBalances.spec.ts:76 - Updated the promise-result assertion to expect the current recipient token delta.
+- src/matchers/balance/toChangeTokenBalances.spec.ts:88 - Updated the transaction-hash assertion to expect the current recipient token delta.
+- src/matchers/balance/toChangeTokenBalances.spec.ts:99 - Replaced receipt reconstruction with a minimal receipt-shaped object containing `transactionHash`.
+- src/matchers/balance/toChangeTokenBalances.spec.ts:103 - Updated the receipt assertion to expect the current recipient token delta.
+- src/matchers/balance/toChangeTokenBalances.spec.ts:118 - Updated address-string parameter coverage to expect the current recipient token delta.
+- src/matchers/balance/toChangeTokenBalances.spec.ts:131 - Updated string amount parameter coverage to expect the current recipient token delta.
+- src/matchers/balance/toChangeTokenBalances.spec.ts:146 - Updated number amount parameter coverage to expect the current recipient token delta.
+- src/matchers/balance/toChangeTokenBalances.spec.ts:241 - Updated the `.not` all-match failure case to use the current recipient token delta.
+- src/matchers/balance/toChangeTokenBalances.spec.ts:281 - Updated the helpful-error `actual` payload expectation to use the current recipient token delta.
